# Switch the active behaviour at runtime. Project 05 keeps the three project-02
# obstacle behaviours and adds three vision behaviours that condition on the new
# camera topics. All are mutually exclusive; switch freely.
#
#   1 = obstacle: stop + timer            (pub-sub)            [from 02]
#   2 = obstacle: stop + random turn      (pub-sub)            [from 02]
#   3 = obstacle: service + escape action (srv + action)       [from 02]
#   4 = light-seek: steer toward brighter (/camera/light_level)
#   5 = colour-seek: chase a target hue   (/camera/mean_color)
#   6 = ArUco: search then approach marker (srv + ApproachMarker action)
int8 behavior
---
bool success
string message
